snippet.title: Behind the Stumbles Part 2: The Big Show
snippet.description:
Welcome to the big show! In this episode of Behind the Stumbles, some of the Fall Guys team make their way to PAX East to find out which of the guests can make their way to the top of the mountain! 

Coming to PlayStation 4 and Steam this summer! 
Wishlist: http://fallguys.com
Discord: https://discordapp.com/invite/fallguys
